720234f-a.text:
Greenwich Street, south from West Houston Street as photographed from the uptown "El' platform. Shown are the tracks and station of the 9th Avenue "El" obliterating details of the street below. Buildings shown are on the west side of dreenwich Street.
These are mainly warehouses and lofts.
May 7, 1940
Views 1,2
P. L. Sperr
720234f-a.folder: Greenwich Street & Houston Street (West), Manhattan, NY

720235f-a.text:
Greenwich Street, at West Houston Street, showing details of the 9th Avenue 'El" station and tracks at this point. The photographer is standing on the downtown platform and is viewing eastward towards that one opposite. Demolition of this structure and
its appurtenances is shortly to occur.
June 7, 1940
Views 1,2,3
P. L. Sperr
720235f-a.folder: Greenwich Street & Houston Street (West), Manhattan, NY
